summary: I haven’t seen any of the Marvel movies and I really want to experience seeing End Game in theaters because it’s such a world...
body:
I haven’t seen any of the Marvel movies and I really want to experience seeing End Game in theaters because it’s such a world wide phenomenon right now. So, I’m bingeing the entire Marvel series rn to see End Game in two weeks. Which also means that I’m live blogging my reactions because a girl is hella behind and confused. (I am watching them in the recommended order for understanding.)

I’ve already seen Captain America: The First Avenger, Captain Marvel and Iron Man 1 in the last four days.

title: Prognostication
body:
by Iron_Daddy

Sort of Spoilers but not bc its an AU???
-
-
-

When Peter holds the gauntlet in his hands, he doesn’t give it up.

Instead he puts it on, snaps his fingers and yeets Thanos.

A.K.A
An Endgame AU where Peter suspects the outcome of the battle and decides to take it upon himself to snap his fingers instead, regardless of the cost. He’ll do whatever it takes to keep Mr Stark safe.

title: Panthera Onca - Chapter 20
excerpt: An Archive of Our Own, a project of the Organization for Transformative Works
description:
“Okay,” Steve said and looked at the agents and the few Avengers with him. “The traces led to this park. You all know the plan and…”

He could never finish his sentence because that moment Thor landed right beside him in a huge ray of light.

—

Yes, it’s 5 years since I updated the story but I promised a new chapter to all unfinished stories and here we go :D
